---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
import Navigation from "../components/Navigation.astro";
---

<MainLayout title="Tasting Methodology | Enoversa">
    <Navigation />

    <main class="pt-32 pb-24 px-6 md:px-24 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <header class="mb-24 border-b border-line pb-12">
            <span
                class="font-mono text-xs text-accent uppercase tracking-widest mb-4 block"
                >The Framework</span
            >
            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-light tracking-tighter mb-8">
                Structural <span class="italic font-serif text-text-dim"
                    >Methodology.</span
                >
            </h1>
            <p
                class="text-xl font-light text-text-muted max-w-2xl leading-relaxed"
            >
                We do not score wines on a 100-point scale. Instead, we analyze
                their kinetic and structural architecture using a 3-point system
                (0—2).
            </p>
        </header>

        <div class="space-y-24">
            <!-- Metric 1 -->
            <section class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-12">
                <div class="md:col-span-4">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-light text-white mb-2">
                        01. Liveliness / Energy
                    </h2>
                    <p class="font-mono text-xs text-text-dim">
                        KINETIC TENSION
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="md:col-span-8 space-y-6">
                    <p class="text-text-muted font-light">
                        How much kinetic tension does the wine have? Acidity,
                        texture, aromatic movement, and "inner light".
                    </p>
                    <div
                        class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 font-mono text-xs border-t border-line pt-4"
                    >
                        <div>
                            <span class="text-accent block mb-1"
                                >0 - Static</span
                            >Heavy, dull, closed.
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <span class="text-accent block mb-1"
                                >1 - Moderate</span
                            >Some tension, signs of life.
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <span class="text-accent block mb-1"
                                >2 - Electric</span
                            >Vibration, lift, crystalline movement.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- Metric 2 -->
            <section class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-12">
                <div class="md:col-span-4">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-light text-white mb-2">
                        02. Drinkability / Purity
                    </h2>
                    <p class="font-mono text-xs text-text-dim">
                        FLUIDITY & TRANSPARENCY
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="md:col-span-8 space-y-6">
                    <p class="text-text-muted font-light">
                        How clean, unforced, and drinkable the wine feels.
                        Absence of distractions (excess extraction, oak, brett).
                    </p>
                    <div
                        class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 font-mono text-xs border-t border-line pt-4"
                    >
                        <div>
                            <span class="text-accent block mb-1"
                                >0 - Fatiguing</span
                            >Hard to drink, distracting flaws.
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <span class="text-accent block mb-1">1 - Clean</span
                            >Good purity, nothing tiring.
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <span class="text-accent block mb-1"
                                >2 - Crystalline</span
                            >Transparent, fluid, irresistible.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- Metric 3 -->
            <section class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-12">
                <div class="md:col-span-4">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-light text-white mb-2">
                        03. Balance
                    </h2>
                    <p class="font-mono text-xs text-text-dim">
                        STRUCTURAL HARMONY
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="md:col-span-8 space-y-6">
                    <p class="text-text-muted font-light">
                        Harmony among structural components (acid, tannin,
                        alcohol, texture) and between nose & palate.
                    </p>
                    <div
                        class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 font-mono text-xs border-t border-line pt-4"
                    >
                        <div>
                            <span class="text-accent block mb-1"
                                >0 - Disharmony</span
                            >Elements clash or dominate.
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <span class="text-accent block mb-1"
                                >1 - Harmonious</span
                            >Mostly integrated, minor unevenness.
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <span class="text-accent block mb-1"
                                >2 - Complete</span
                            >Seamless integration.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- Metric 4 -->
            <section class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-12">
                <div class="md:col-span-4">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-light text-white mb-2">
                        04. Complexity
                    </h2>
                    <p class="font-mono text-xs text-text-dim">
                        RANGE & EVOLUTION
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="md:col-span-8 space-y-6">
                    <p class="text-text-muted font-light">
                        Range and evolution of aromas, textures, and flavours
                        over time.
                    </p>
                    <div
                        class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 font-mono text-xs border-t border-line pt-4"
                    >
                        <div>
                            <span class="text-accent block mb-1"
                                >0 - Simple</span
                            >One-dimensional.
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <span class="text-accent block mb-1"
                                >1 - Layered</span
                            >Several dimensions; gentle evolution.
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <span class="text-accent block mb-1">2 - Deep</span
                            >Multiple layers, long evolution over time.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- Metric 5 -->
            <section class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-12">
                <div class="md:col-span-4">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-light text-white mb-2">
                        05. Emotion
                    </h2>
                    <p class="font-mono text-xs text-text-dim">RESONANCE</p>
                </div>
                <div class="md:col-span-8 space-y-6">
                    <p class="text-text-muted font-light">
                        How deeply the wine resonates beyond its technical
                        qualities — its ability to create memory, contemplation,
                        or intimacy.
                    </p>
                    <div
                        class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 font-mono text-xs border-t border-line pt-4"
                    >
                        <div>
                            <span class="text-accent block mb-1">0 - None</span
                            >No personal connection.
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <span class="text-accent block mb-1"
                                >1 - Suggestive</span
                            >A moment of recognition or nostalgia.
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <span class="text-accent block mb-1"
                                >2 - Profound</span
                            >Changes your mood or sense of time.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
        </div>
    </main>
</MainLayout>
